00:21:41.990 --> 00:21:44.120
are lots of studies
done on similar topics.

00:21:44.120 --> 00:21:46.950
And some of them point
towards one direction.

00:21:46.950 --> 00:21:49.800
Others point towards a
different direction, et cetera.

00:21:49.800 --> 00:21:51.383
MALCOLM GLADWELL:
Well, you're looking

00:21:51.383 --> 00:21:54.580
for trends in the research.

00:21:54.580 --> 00:21:57.810
And so, for example,
the studies I

00:21:57.810 --> 00:21:59.820
was just mentioning
