00:22:27.330 --> 00:22:29.940
But there's no shortage.

00:22:29.940 --> 00:22:31.940
I mean, the thing that's
fascinating about being

00:22:31.940 --> 00:22:35.890
a sort of student
of academic research

00:22:35.890 --> 00:22:41.920
is that the number of things
that on an academic level--

00:22:41.920 --> 00:22:47.040
ideas that are being
pursued and conclusions

00:22:47.040 --> 00:22:50.760
