00:23:04.500 --> 00:23:05.830
I mean, it's not hard to do.

00:23:05.830 --> 00:23:12.240
So to me, what always
amazes me, is how much

00:23:12.240 --> 00:23:16.010
fascinating and
useful material lies

00:23:16.010 --> 00:23:19.190
buried in academia, just
never sees the light of day

00:23:19.190 --> 00:23:24.247
because no one bothers
to go and write about it

00:23:24.247 --> 00:23:25.080
and popularizing it.

00:23:25.080 --> 00:23:28.200
I mean, it's astounding
how-- you know,

00:23:28.200 --> 00:23:33.254
if you talk to academics,
the list of things

00:23:33.254 --> 00:23:35.670
that they think that the rest
of the world is doing wrong,

00:23:35.670 --> 00:23:38.640
it's like this long.

00:23:38.640 --> 00:23:43.646
So it's not a very
